# Input

```yml
# Outside flow collection:
- ::vector
- ": - ()"
- Up, up, and away!
- -123
- http://example.com/foo#bar
# Inside flow collection:
- [ ::vector,
  ": - ()",
  "Up, up and away!",
  -123,
  http://example.com/foo#bar ]

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -5,4 +5,8 @@
 - -123
 - http://example.com/foo#bar
 # Inside flow collection:
-- [::vector, ": - ()", "Up, up and away!", -123, http://example.com/foo#bar]
+- [ ::vector,
+  ": - ()",
+  "Up, up and away!",
+  -123,
+  http://example.com/foo#bar ]
```

